#!/usr/bin/env bash
set -euo pipefail

cat <<'EOF'
NeuroOS updates (MVP scaffold)

- System image updates:
    For now, update by replacing the VM disk image artifact (qcow2) and using VM snapshots for rollback.

- App updates:
    Flatpak:  flatpak update
    Web/PWA:  updated by origin/runtime

- Catalog metadata:
    In this repo, catalog/index.json is designed to be signed and verified.
    See docs/updates.md for the model.
EOF

